        "id": 1157909
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-11-24T22:05:56Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yeah I think we should have bother exported and parent invocation ids (and probably realms?). But I\u0027m not sure about invocation tags, will we ever need invocation tags in the artifact table? I think the common usage of this table is to join with the result table.",
      "parentUuid": "9c608336_a4310a83",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 25,
        "startChar": 2,
        "endLine": 25,
        "endChar": 26
